quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  19,1,"Kaf-ha-ya-AAayn-sad"
  19,2,"Thikru rahmati rabbika AAabdahuzakariyya"
  19,3,"Ith nada rabbahu nidaankhafiyya"
  19,4,"Qala rabbi innee wahana alAAathmuminnee washtaAAala arra/su shayban walam akunbiduAAa-ika rabbi shaqiyya"
  19,5,"Wa-innee khiftu almawaliya min wara-eewakanati imraatee AAaqiran fahab lee min ladunkawaliyya"
  19,6,"Yarithunee wayarithu min ali yaAAqoobawajAAalhu rabbi radiyya"
  19,7,"Ya zakariyya innanubashshiruka bighulamin ismuhu yahya lamnajAAal lahu min qablu samiyya"
  19,8,"Qala rabbi anna yakoonu leeghulamun wakanati imraatee AAaqiran waqadbalaghtu mina alkibari AAitiyya"
  19,9,"Qala kathalika qalarabbuka huwa AAalayya hayyinun waqad khalaqtuka min qablu walamtaku shay-a"
  19,10,"Qala rabbi ijAAal lee ayatan qalaayatuka alla tukallima annasa thalathalayalin sawiyya"